      "content": "Subject: Your Application for the Senior Developer Position\n\nDear [Candidate's Name],\n\nThank you for taking the time to interview for the Senior Developer position at [Company Name]. We appreciate the effort you put into the interview process and the insights you shared about your expertise in system design and your positive cultural fit with our team.\n\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with another candidate whose experience aligns more closely with our specific cloud stack needs. This decision was not an easy one, as we were truly impressed by your skills and potential.\n\nWe hope you understand our decision and wish you all the best in your future endeavors. We value the opportunity to have worked with you and believe you have a bright future ahead.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Company Name]  \n[Contact Information]",
